room_title: Escape room "Hijacked At Sea" by 321 Escape Rooms in Melbourne
review: I had a fun experience at 321Escape with the Hijacked at Sea escape room. The puzzles were fun and challenging. The staff was great and engaging. I am looking forward to challenging the other rooms with my friends.

room_title: Escape room "Hijacked At Sea" by 321 Escape Rooms in Melbourne
review: The cruise hijack room was awesome. Looking forward to coming back and trying heist and escape from space!

room_title: Escape room "Hijacked At Sea" by 321 Escape Rooms in Melbourne
review: We had a great experience at 321 Escape, and the staff is super helpful. The Hijacked at Sea room is challenging but has a great setup of decor and puzzles. I've done about 15 escape rooms and this was def one of my favorites.
